<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> The 6-inch number appears in <i>Wilderness</i> p. 36-37, but given the original 3.5 inch bore of the 25 pounder, this is unlikely. More likely candidates are the <a href="/wiki/BL_5.5_inch_Medium_Gun" title="BL 5.5 inch Medium Gun">BL 5.5 inch Medium Gun</a> or <a href="/wiki/6_inch_26_cwt_howitzer" title="6 inch 26 cwt howitzer">6 inch 26 cwt howitzer</a>. Another possibility is that the 6" number is incorrect, a 4" would have been possible with the 25-pdr.</li>
